278
00:40:17,360 --> 00:40:19,039
[SPEAKER_02] Ja kažem kako mišljenje za javna smaknuća.

279
00:40:19,199 --> 00:40:20,639
[SPEAKER_02] Ne, imate video, pogledajte video.

280
00:40:20,880 --> 00:40:37,119
